name: Vladimir Putin dressed as the Easter Bunny trending on ArtStation
description:
The title was the input to VQGAN+CLIP while @clayheaton was testing library parameters. The output was this glorious image of Easter Putin and his ripped bunny thighs. Get your Easter baskets ready, children!

Upon seeing the image, @sableraph guessed the input phrase exactly. This is a commemorative mint of that stroke of genius.
